#### Issue details
I use libgdx with rxjava with GdxScheulder that schedule tasks via `Gdx.app.postRunnable`.

There is `AndroidGraphics.java` sources's part: 

```
			for (int i = 0; i < app.getExecutedRunnables().size; i++) {
